cs.IT, cs.AR, cs.SY, cs.MM, cs.NI 

This paper deals with the comparison of different receiver architectures for mmWave systems, which involves information theory (cs.IT), signal processing (cs.AR), control systems (cs.SY), wireless communications (cs.MM), and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the trade-off between energy and spectral efficiency, which is a common theme in these sub-categories.
